<plot>Chandler owns and runs one of the finest bed &amp; breakfasts in town. What his guests do not realize, is that each room is secretly monitored by a hidden video camera. He delights in entering the very private worlds of those who pass through, and when the Glue family arrives, he uncovers their well kept secret. In this short dramatic film, which combines stop-motion animation with live-action, dark truths are brought to the surface, not only for the Glue family, but very unexpectedly, for Chandler himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?062910</url></doc>
